disposal of the last sizeable chunk of the Ferranti businesses.
Ferranti Information &amp; Response Systems is based in Wythenshawe, Manchester
and employs about 150 people. It designs, develops and maintains systems for
airport information, baggage reclaim, flight information and displays,
flight message switching and emergency services command and control.
