FT  29 NOV 94 / Lib Dems face 'low brand loyalty'
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By RAYMOND SNODDY
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Taylor Nelson AGB, the UK's biggest market research group, has found some
bad news for the Liberal Democrats, Raymond Snoddy writes.
